  },
  {
    "module": "trust_scoring.py",
    "severity": "medium",
    "issue": "Lines 195-196: `except Exception: continue` silently swallows all receipt-loading errors in `compute_from_receipts`. Corrupt files, permission errors, and schema mismatches are all invisible."
